Flung back from the shot by Tyrael. "AAAARRRGGGHHHHHH!!!!" Then slid across 
the ground. 

Weak now, she drew from what power she had left, Attempting to get up. 

"Tyrael," sh said weakly, "You.. talk.. too... much!" she growled at him. 
Then collapsed. Laying there. Damaged & low on power. This form was not as tough 
as her older form. 

She still considered Tyrael more than a fool. Laying there a moment, then she 
attempted to get up again. Once more, she collapsed. Again, she tried... & 
yet again, she collapsed. She gave up for the moment, too tired to try again. 


--part1_21.320bd0a5.2c421691_boundary
